-Free\ntwo-photon absorption spectra, which will dramatically increase the selectivity\nof trace gas detection of samples with multiple components with overlapping\nabsorption bands. This is demonstrated by the predicted mid-IR two-photon\nabsorption spectrum of butadiene using theoretical spectroscopic constants.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 1 Aug 2019 22:03:41 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 10 Oct 2019 21:05:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-10-14"}
