rizations even in this more classical setting, also\nunderlying connections with the notion of an elementary cogenerator.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 1 Aug 2019 22:44:29 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 11 Feb 2021 15:59:48 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 28 Jul 2022 17:51:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-29"}
